CONTEXT RightResidualTypeCheck IN ENGLISH

PURPOSE CONTEXT RightResidualTypeCheck
{+ Test that right residual succeeds when sources can be joined.
   This verifies the type checker correctly accepts r~[B*A]\s[B*C] yielding [A*C]. +}

RELATION r[A*B]
RELATION s[B*C]
RELATION result[A*C]

RULE testRightResidual: result = r~\s

ENDCONTEXT
